<H2><IMG SRC="../GFX/edu.gif"><FONT COLOR="yellow"><b>Интервью с Nicholas Blachford</b></FONT><IMG SRC="../GFX/edu.gif"></H2><BR>

<table border="1" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" width="80%" bordercolorlight="#5091F3" bordercolordark="#000000">
